OL,5, People are being alerted to the fire   
OL,6, risks of unsafe use of electric heaters
OL,7, as they try to keep down costs during  
OL,8, the winter.                            
OL,10,FThe popularity of portable machines to 
OL,11,Fheat a single room has increased as    
OL,12,Fenergy bills have soared.              
OL,14,FBut charity Electrical Safety First has
OL,15,Fhighlighted the dangers of leaving the 
OL,16,Fheaters unattended, on unstable        
OL,17,Fsurfaces, or when used to dry clothes. 
OL,19,FFirefighters described shocking cases, 
OL,20,Fsome of which have led to deaths.      
